We`re looking to be one big, happy, healthy household!! Roommates will share weekly cleaning duties but nothing sinister, just the usual "time-to-vacuum-and-clean-the-bathroom/kitchen" thing. If you`ve been in a shared living situation before you`ll feel right at home but you must definitely be OK with keeping the place reasonably clean.
No lease is required and no pesky 1st and last--$150 deposit is required along with 1st month`s rent for a total of $490 for the first month, which will be pro-rated if necessary.

I probably will not respond to boring one-sentence emails so have a heart and describe yourself a bit.
This is a recycling household which means be prepared to do your part for the environment.
Cheers!
